Ein Warideh ()  is a Syrian village located in Al-Suqaylabiyah Nahiyah in Al-Suqaylabiyah District, Hama.  According to the Syria Central Bureau of Statistics (CBS), Ein Warideh had a population of 468 in the 2004 census.
